//  OUTPUT FILES :
//		BaseFlow.txt			-> base flow (FF format)
//      BaseFlow.ff2m         -> base flow (FF2M format) 
//
// 	ERROR MANAGEMENT : 
//      if Newton iteration diverges, BaseFlow.txt is not generated and "iter" parameter in BaseFlow.ff2m is -1.
//
//
